<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Hydrologic processes rather than fire primarily disturb stands. Managers use fire in the late summer or fall to clear vegetation in managed wetlands, such as in parts of Suisun Marsh. Altered hydrology, unnatural fire and clearing may initiate stands of this non-native type.</div>
